						<div class="bee-text-content" style="line-height: 120%; font-size: 12px; font-family: inherit; color: #555555;">
							<p style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 14px; text-align: left;">The WISER Staff and Kenyan and US boards welcome Alex Schvartsburg as our newest US Board Member. Alex is the Chief Financial Officer of <a href="https://investor.livanova.com" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline;" target="_blank">LivaNova,</a> a global medical technology company with headquarters in London and Texas.</p>
							<p style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 14px; text-align: left;"> </p>
							<p style="line-height: 14px;">Mr. Shvartsburg brings his vast financial planning expertise to the WISER family. Prior to his appointment as Chief Financial Officer, he led the LivaNova Corporate Financial Planning and Analysis group and was the International Region CFO. Before joining LivaNova in 2017, Mr. Shvartsburg was CFO and Chief Operating Officer of Caligor, a private equity-backed clinical services organization, where he was responsible for Finance, Operations, Human Resources and Information Technology functions. Before that, he held finance leadership roles including CFO of the Genetic Sciences division at Thermo Fisher Scientific, Senior Finance Director M&amp;A at Life Technologies, and for over 20 years, Mr. Shvartsburg held a series of finance roles of increasing responsibility within Johnson &amp; Johnson.</p>
							<p style="line-height: 14px;"> </p>
							<p style="line-height: 14px;">Mr. Shvartsburg earned a Bachelor of Science degree in Accounting from Drexel University and a Master of Business Administration from LaSalle University, and he is a Certified Management Accountant.</p>
							<p style="line-height: 14px;"> </p>
							<p style="line-height: 14px;">You can congratulate Alex by congratulations on his new position by posting on WISER’s <a href="https://www.facebook.com/WISERGirlsKenya" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline;" target="_blank"><strong style="">Facebook</strong></a>, <a href="https://www.instagram.com/wiser_international" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline;" target="_blank"><strong style="">Instagram</strong></a>, <strong style=""><a href="https://twitter.com/WISERGirls_Intl" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline;" target="_blank">Twitter</a>,</strong> or <strong style=""><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/wiserinternational" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline;" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a></strong> pages. You can also help us welcome Mr. Shvartsburg by <a href="https://wisergirls.org/ways_to_donate" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration: underline;" target="_blank"><strong style="">making a donation</strong></a> and showing your support for WISER’s new leadership! Your financial support helps us accomplish our important work for the hardest to reach girls. </p>
